snippet.title: Stray Blade Launches April 20, 2023 (ESRB)
snippet.description:
Stray Blade launches globally on April 20, 2023 on Steam, Epic, PS5 & XSX.

Wishlist Stray Blade to stay up to date on all big updates, community happenings, and more. https://505.games/SteamSB

Last call to register for the Stray Blade Beta! This is your chance to be among the first to play Stray Blade. All Beta Testers will also be featured in the game credits!

Register for the Stray Blade Beta here: https://505.games/SBBeta

Chat live with the official Stray Blade community on Discord at http://505.games/SBDiscord or join the Stray Blade subreddit at https://505.games/SBReddit

Visit the Stray Blade website for all other details: http://www.stray-blade.com
